  <h2>What Most Gardeners Should Actually Use</h2>

  <p>
    Use small, flexible clips and apply them early as cucumber vines begin to climb. Focus on gentle support and frequent placement rather than strong gripping force.
  </p>

  <p>
    This keeps growth controlled without stressing the plant.
  </p>

  <p class="muted">
    Guide early, and the plant follows.
